agents_only.template:
Recommend one of the following subagents be utilized in servicing this request:
{agent_list}

However, if your assessment based on the full context of the request is that these subagents are not appropriate, do not over- or mis-delegate.

agents_and_skills.template:
You MUST delegate to one of these subagents:
{agent_list}

Craft a detailed Task prompt as you normally would, then APPEND skill instructions. The subagent should invoke these skills: {skill_list}

Append to your Task prompt: "Use the Skill tool to invoke [skill-name] for the relevant functionality. Report which skill(s) you used."

If these agents/skills are clearly irrelevant, use your judgment.

skills_only.template:
You SHOULD use the following skill(s) for this request: {skill_list}

Invoke with: Skill(skill="[skill-name]")

If delegating to a subagent, instruct them to invoke the skill and report back which they used. If you used any of these skills, note which ones in your response.
